About this item

  • Please Note: Your ecobee smart thermostat will came with an original wall plate. Unlike the original equipped bracket, our gorgeous decorative Ecobee Smart Thermostat Premium/ Enhanced wall plate with elegant matte surface perfectly creates a modern and stylish look, covers up the previous hole or mark.
  • Designed exclusively for 2022 Ecobee Smart Thermostat Premium and 2022 Ecobee Smart Thermostat Enhanced. It will not fit any other Ecobee Thermostat. Please check your Thermostat model firstly before purchasing it.
  • Installation can be finished in a few minutes. No need to paint or do any remodeling work to install the wall plate for your 2022 Ecobee smart thermostat.
  • Our Ecobee wall mounting plate made of polycarbonate material to provide durability and flexibility to withstand any heavy force.
  • Package Included one 6.14*6.14 inches (15.6*15.6 CM) Ecobee wall plate and screw sets. Please Note: The Ecobee Thermostat is not included.

Product Description

OUR STORY

CaseBot, a premium series brought to you by Fintie!

How we got our start?

Founded in Columbus Ohio, Fintie LLC brings you stylish and high quality products and accessories for home furnishing. We have been in the home furnishing product business for over 15 years and directly manufacture most of the popular products we sell.

What makes our product unique?

We believe customers are looking for reasonably priced products but without any sacrifice on quality. Our aim is to reach every single customer that falls into this group with our quality products. Our direct sales model without a middleman allows us to pass significant savings to our customers.

Why we love what we do?

Since we control our own production runs, we take great pride in our ability to constantly excite our customers with new product designs and styles. Our reliable customer support team is here to help you with any questions you have about your purchase or the products we offer.

Fit Module:

2022 Ecobee Smart Thermostat Premium

2022 Ecobee Smart Thermostat Enhanced

Not Fit Module:

ecobee SmartThermostat with VoiceControl 2019: EB-STATE5-01

ecobee4: EB-STATE4-01

ecobee3 lite 2016: EB-STATe3L-01

ecobee3 (1st generation) 2014: EB-ecobee3-01

ecobee3 (2nd generation) 2015: EB-STATe3-02

Installation

1. Drill two holes on the wall and install the expansion tube into the holes.

2. Align the wall plate with the the thermostat panel.

3. Screws through the expansion tube to fix the wall plate and the thermostat panel.

4. Put the thermostat on the panel of the thermostat.

How customer reviews and ratings work

Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.
